---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — Free Prompt Studio" description="Terms of Service for Free Prompt Studio — a free, browser-based AI prompt engineering toolkit.">
  <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-tertiary">Last updated: June 2026</p>

  <section class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">By using Free Prompt Studio, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the service.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">Free Prompt Studio is a static, browser-based prompt engineering toolkit. All processing happens locally in your browser — no data is sent to any server.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">3. No Data Collection</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">We do not collect, store, or process any personal data. Theme preferences and dismissed banners are stored locally in your browser via localStorage and never transmitted.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">4. No Warranties</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">This service is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We make no guarantees about the accuracy or usefulness of generated prompts.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">We shall not be liable for any damages arising from your use of this service.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">6. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">We may update these terms at any time. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-base font-medium text-primary">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-1">For questions about these terms, please open an issue on our GitHub repository.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
